plot outline: Nenu Lenu is the story of Eeshwar (Harshit), an orphan who falls for Parvati's (Sri Padma) honesty in the first sight and convinces her to marry him after much effort. In time, a gang of goons hunt for him and take him away. Later, news comes out that Eeshwar killed three of them and one is missing. Cops find Eeshwar under mysterious circumstances and are shocked when he claims to be already dead.
title: Nenu Lenu
